    "new_prompt_text": "Solve the question directly.\nKeep the entire JSON compact.\nKeep decision_notes extremely short. Prefer 3 to 8 words.\nDo not narrate your reasoning outside the response field.\nIn the response field, use exactly two short lines encoded with \\n:\nFINAL_ANSWER: <answer>\nJUSTIFICATION: <brief justification>\nKeep the justification to 12 words or fewer.\nUse plain text only inside the response field. Do not use markdown formatting, code fences, or math-style backslashes such as \\equiv.\nDo not add any extra text before or after the JSON object.\n\nReturn exactly one JSON object in this format:\n{\n  \"schema_name\": \"eywa_node_response\",\n  \"schema_version\": \"v1\",\n  \"orchestration_decision\": \"execute_locally\",\n  \"decision_notes\": \"optional string\",\n  \"response\": \"FINAL_ANSWER: <answer>\\nJUSTIFICATION: <brief justification>\",\n  \"result_type\": \"summary\"\n}"
  },
